Folia succuba, parum inclinata, patentia, parumper adscendentia, plana, ovalia aut ovali-oblonga, in dorso parumper decurrentia nec medium caulem attingentia, in ventre magis adhuc distantia: inferiora minora et dissita, superiora caulium maiora semiliueam fere longa et imbricata, ramorum inferiora minima, alia hinc adproximata‚ pleraque apice truncato-aut subretuso-bidentata, alia amentata, denticulis ubicunque parvis mucronuliformibus, inferiora folia quandoque et obtusa, mutica aut altero fine unidentula.
